msgctxt "84_Ex-Tojo Yakuza"
msgid "Watch out, Saejima-san. Hamazaki's taking you for the ride of the century."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96_Saejima"
msgid "Whaddya mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108_Ex-Tojo Yakuza"
msgid "I used to be in the Tojo, just like you... and lemme tell you, nothing good's gonna come from trusting that dirty two-timer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120_Ex-Tojo Yakuza"
msgid "Did you know he and the Snake Flower Triad tried taking over the Tojo? Needless to say, more than a few guys in here would love nothing more than to stick a knife in his belly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Saejima"
msgid "Ya got beef with Hamazaki, take it up with him. Don't got nothin' to do with me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144_Ex-Tojo Yakuza"
msgid "Not sure that's true. Lemme guess, he said he's gonna help you break out? Sorry, pal, but he's gonna sell you out first chance he gets. You'll see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168_Ex-Tojo Yakuza"
msgid "Look, I'm just trying to warn you. Back out now before shit really hits the fan."
msgstr ""

